precis:
Enactment of the ORGANIZATION OF AMERICAN STATES PRIVILEGES AND IMMUNITIES
IN CANADA ORDER - which provides that this organization shall, in Canada,
have the legal capacities of a body corporate, and certain privileges and
immunities set out in the Convention on the Privileges and Immunities of
the United Nations.
